Name: Average time from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time between First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Minimum time it takes First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to be followed by Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average time for First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation when preceded by First Look-Your updates are overdue
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Time from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to the next occurrence of Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average waiting time to First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation after First Look-Your updates are due in one week
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look-Your updates are due in one week' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Minimum time between First Look-Please submit updates and First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time it takes First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to occur after First Look-Your updates are overdue in accepted manuscript variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' and activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Average time from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to the end of the case (last recorded activity)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to lead to Manuscript Export Succeeded in variants ending with acceptance
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time between First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the final Manuscript Export Succeeded in multi-revision submission paths

Name: Time from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Awaiting Assignment to Batch compared to the time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
